Keylogger Consent Form
Purpose of Consent: This form is to obtain your consent for the monitoring of your activities on Company-owned devices through keylogging software.

1. Acknowledgment
I, 			acknowledge that I have been informed that the Company may install keylogging software on my Company-owned devices, including computers, laptops, and mobile devices.

2. Nature of Monitoring
I			 understand that this software will monitor and record all keystrokes, including but not limited to emails, instant messages, and other digital communications during work hours.

3. Purpose of Monitoring
I 			understand that the purpose of this monitoring is to ensure compliance with Company policies, protect Company assets, and enhance productivity.

4. Data Handling
I 			acknowledge that the recorded data will be handled in accordance with applicable laws and regulations regarding data protection and privacy.

5. Consent
By signing below, I provide my consent for the installation and use of keylogging software on my Company-owned devices.

